mysql connector,mongoDB CONNECTOR, json jar, testNG

what is dependency injection in java?
A. dependency injection is when a object contains the dependencies of another object and is passed to it so that it
can use it.

What is static binding and dynamic binding?
A.static binding refers to the calls that can be resolved at compilation time while, dynamic binding are the calls
that can be resolved only at runtime.









